name: Juicy Buds Phuket
description: Juicy Buds offers the highest grade of medical Cannabis in Thailand. We are located on Bangla Road next to Sugar Club Complex and Central Patong.

products_flowers.name: Gary Payton
products_flowers.description: Named the famous point guard ‘The Glove’, this flavourful strain hits like a boxer and warms like a glove. Offering a strong gassy, floral aroma and pungent buttery taste, it’s easy to see why Gary Payton is top choice for connoisseurs.

products_flowers.name: Juicy Gold
products_flowers.description: A proprietary cross from the Thailand Dank Squad, Juicy Gold was created especially for Juicy Buds. It is a superb smoke that leaves the user with an uplifted, clear-headed, and lucid high. Psychedelic at it’s core, Juicy Gold is perfect for a big night out with friends.

products_flowers.name: Blue Zuchi
products_flowers.description: Deep blueberry fragrance with gassy hints of ammonia. This indica-dominant strain offers a flavour profile reminiscent of sour diesel and classic skunk. Blue Zushi produces a buzzy head high ideal for light smokers or as a goto bud for daily use.

products_flowers.name: Platinum Dolato
products_flowers.description: This sweet indica-dominant variety offers a pungent, earthy scent with caramel undertones and hints of vanilla. Beginners can expect heaps of laughter with a calming after buzz, whilst experienced users can enjoy a clear, creative focus perfect for getting things done.

products_flowers.name: Gusher Mintz
products_flowers.description: A delicate hybrid that has a calming and stress relieving effect, while also heightening sensory perception. The hype strain parentage creates a unique flavor profile that is both Minty and fruity, yet has a deep earthy exhale that is sure to delight.

products_flowers.name: Red Velvet
products_flowers.description: A newer hype strain that dazzles users with it’s amazing cinnamon aroma. This variety stands out as an all around hybrid that gives users the pain relief of an Indica with the energy of a Sativa. Perfect for the bedroom.

products_flowers.name: Bubba's Cookies
products_flowers.description: Bubba’s Cookies can play on any team. Whether you need a relaxing evening at home, or you want to tear up the dance floor, Bubba’s Cookies has the versatility and mood enhancement that will keep you engaged in anything for hours. Users report increased focus, a calmer mood, increased confidence, and general sensory enhancement.

products_flowers.name: Zkittlez
products_flowers.description: There is perhaps no more hyped variety than Zkittlez in the last five years, and for a good reason. Despite its heavy Indica parentage, Zkittlez is anything but your typical Indica. Users report feeling increased focus and an even keel while enjoying a perfectly relaxing high that compliments the end of the day wonderfully.

products_flowers.name: Blue Sunset Sherbet
products_flowers.description: Uplifting and joyous variety known for providing relaxation as well as an easy-going feeling that all Cannabis consumers desire. Whether a seasoned connoisseur or a casual weekend warrior, Blue Sunset Sherbet Shines as a great all around strain.

products_flowers.name: Lemon Chello
products_flowers.description: Uplifting and joyous variety known for providing relaxation as well as an easy-going feeling that all Cannabis consumers desire. Whether a seasoned connoisseur or a casual weekend warrior, Blue Sunset Sherbet Shines as a great all around strain.

reviews.author: Hecto Rious
reviews.content:
OMG! I've met my new family... Really helpful and knowledgeable as to what would work best for my insomnia.

Gold stars all around!!!

reviews.author: Behzad Rad
reviews.content: Very nice beautiful design i like it , buds and strains good looking and price for patong with that quality is amazing , lady bud tender very beautiful smart and have enough knowledge about cannabis and very helpful ❤️, 🪩 dont forgot to visit if you in bangla

reviews.author: Florian Brasseur
reviews.content: Lot of choices and very good quality, nice place to smoke and chill, with very helpful staff 👍👍

reviews.author: Moetheninja
reviews.content: Amazing friendly staffs, amazing selection from many known top shelf/exotic strains and their prices are really low compared to other dispensaries in patong. Highly recommend 👏 Good work guys amazing dispensary

reviews.author: Toby Webmaster
reviews.content: Opening was great very impresed with the clean and efficient layout of the shop. Great location too right in the heart of Bangla road.

reviews.author: Elaine D'Arcy
reviews.content:
I am in a wheelchair and suffer so much pain. In Australia I am prescribed CBD Oil. But it is SOOO expensive. Tried a couple of cigarettes (Oreo Cream) and after 3 puffs I was (almost) pain free. I had to cut the end off and smoked that half during the night. The pain relief was immediate.
I can't take cigarettes to Australia but I'll find out if Jucy's does cannabis oil. Have I found my saviours? I hope so💕🙏

reviews.author: Corey Hurren
reviews.content: Best weed in Phuket, good prices!

reviews.author: Mjuri Dennis
reviews.content: Loved this place! The vibe was great and you are given everything you need. Surprised it wasn’t as busy in there. The salted caramel popcorn is a must try 😮‍💨

reviews.author: meshal og
reviews.content: Very friendly and helpful staff, high quality products and good atmosphere in the bar.
